+	 * holding rq->lock, the cpu isn't yet set to this cpu so the
+	 * lockdep check in task_group() will fail.
+	 *
+	 * Similar case to sched_fork(). / Alternatively we could
+	 * use task_rq_lock() here and obtain the other rq->lock.
+	 *
+	 * Silence PROVE_RCU
